        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\nconst route = $json.routes[0];\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    distance_km: Math.round(route.summary.distance / 1000),\n    duration_hours: Number((route.summary.duration / 3600).toFixed(1))\n  }\n}];"
      },
